Author: Colgate_Grizi7
Text: Hey honestly it’s not your fault, it’s no ones fault apart from the awful ED you have, I know right now you’ll feel like you’re being ungrateful and yes while it isn’t ideal to waste food it also isn’t ideal for you to be suffering like this so we can’t really compare the two situations, would you be able to tell your family about your bulimia more, or is that out of the question?   Stay strong and take care of yourself!!
